This software uses the Tahetorn_9B neural machine translation model developed
by TartuNLP (Natural Language Processing research group at the University of
Tartu), which is based on Unbabel/Tower-Plus-9B and Google's Gemma 2 9B.

Model: tartuNLP/Tahetorn_9B
Source: https://huggingface.co/tartuNLP/Tahetorn_9B
License: CC-BY-NC-SA-4.0 (Creative Commons Attribution-NonCommercial-ShareAlike 4.0 International)

Base Model: Unbabel/Tower-Plus-9B
License: CC-BY-NC-4.0

Base Architecture: Google Gemma 2 9B
License: Gemma Terms of Use (https://ai.google.dev/gemma/terms)

